### android_root_detection
- 严重性: INFO
- 中文解读: 未发现 root 检测能力。若应用依赖设备完整性（安全关键功能），可考虑加入合规的完整性校验，但要注意兼容性与误判。
- 原始描述: This app does not have root detection capabilities. Running a sensitive application on a rooted device questions the device integrity and affects users data.
- 参考: https://github.com/MobSF/owasp-mstg/blob/master/Document/0x05j-Testing-Resiliency-Against-Reverse-Engineering.md#testing-root-detection-mstg-resilience-1

